text: George Bytheway (27 March 1908 – 1979) was an English professional footballer who played in the Football League for Coventry City, Mansfield Town and West Bromwich Albion. ==References== Category:1908 births Category:1979 deaths Category:English footballers Category:Association football forwards Category:English Football League players Category:West Bromwich Albion F.C. players Category:Coventry City F.C. players Category:Mansfield Town F.C. players Category:Guildford City F.C. players
